    <string name="lbControlsHelpBottom">"If you tap a glyph, the declaration of the glyph and the tone that goes with it will be shown.

There is also a widget for the home screen to show the current date."</string>
    <string name="lbControlsHelpTop">In the top bar there are buttons that allow you to quickly change the date. It is possible that you cannot see all the buttons shown here, the number of buttons that you see depend on your screen width:</string>
    <string name="lbCredits">The Dreamspell is originally created by José Argüelles and is maintained by www.lawoftime.org</string>
    <string name="lbGuide">Guide</string>
    <string name="lbHelpIntro">"This app introduces a galactic synchronary oracle built with metaphysics that reflect the energies of specific dates. This is a spiritual oracle for self-awareness, to discover the universe inside you; it is based on the calendars of the Mayan civilization. This oracle has no historic value.

The oracle first shown (Galactic Signature) is always the oracle of today. You can select any date that is important to you. Most people choose their own birthday, but it can be any other special day."</string>
    <string name="lbMenuHelp">Depending on what type of device you have, you have a software menu button or a hardware menu button. Both have the same function, to display the menu.</string>
    <string name="lbMenuItemsHelp">In the menu there are items that provide additional functionality. It is possible that you can not see all of the items shown here, the number of items you see will depend on your screen width.</string>
    <string name="lbNextHelp">This button is used to go to the next day.</string>
    <string name="lbOccult">Occult</string>
    <string name="lbPrevHelp">This button is used to go to the previous day.</string>
