    <string name="strWhatsNewContent">"Version 1.0.0

A complete, modern rebuild of the Dreamspell Calendar.

Features
- Galactic Signature — your kin, tone and solar seal for any day
- Destiny Oracle — the five-kin oracle plus the PSI Chrono hidden seal
- Wavespell — the 13-tone wavespell of the day
- Tzolkin — the full 260-kin matrix with Galactic Activation Portals
- Moon Phase — current lunar phase and illumination
- 13 Moon Calendar — the 13-moon, 28-day year
- Kin Combinator — combine several kins into one, from dates or the Tzolkin
- Codex — Harmonics, Chromatics, and the Human and Planet Holon
- Day stepper and date picker to travel to any day
- Help guide to every screen

Languages
- English
- Spanish
- French
- Dutch
- Russian
- Chinese (Simplified and Traditional)
- Nahuatl
- Yucatec Maya"</string>
